&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://media2.dev.to/dynamic/image/width=800%2Cheight=%2Cfit=scale-down%2Cgravity=auto%2Cformat=auto/https%3A%2F%2Fdev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Fmei1et552xvuhd7p3kqj.png" class="article-body-image-wrapper"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media2.dev.to/dynamic/image/width=800%2Cheight=%2Cfit=scale-down%2Cgravity=auto%2Cformat=auto/https%3A%2F%2Fdev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Fmei1et552xvuhd7p3kqj.png" alt="10d10 Psychic Damage â€” hits all party members" width="800" height="797"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;They're human and they KNOW they need to move fast. The opportunity window!!! If the org doesn't catch the wave, someone else will!!!! Someone else gets that 10x productivity boost!!!!!!!&lt;/p&gt;

